        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "Right away, this is about dollars, not just flags. We can see what is ready to pay, what needs review, and where recovery opportunity or compliance risk is starting to build.",
      "demo_actions": "Point to dollar amounts tied to matched, variance, and disputed invoices. Sort or filter to surface the highest-value exceptions.",
