      },
      "time": "~40s",
      "narrative": "Now compare that with an invoice that does not line up. Here, Waypoint shows the gap clearly and ties it back to the source record, so the team can act on facts instead of email threads and manual checks.",
      "demo_actions": "Open a variance or disputed invoice. Highlight the specific mismatch, such as rate, quantity, milestone, timing, or release status. Show linked evidence and the system's decision rationale.",
      "screenshot": null
    },
