      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "This also scales beyond one invoice at a time. We can run reconciliation across the full set with the relevant IQs turned on, so every invoice is checked against the same standard and the same evidence chain.",
      "demo_actions": "Kick off a batch reconciliation, or return to a completed run. Show the enabled IQs and the progress or result summary.",
